<br>
Varia grips the hilt of the sword with one hand, and puts her other hand on Maytha's leg to keep it still. Then she pulls the sword up and the blade smooths itself up and out of Maytha's flesh, leaving a gaping hole gushing blood. She quickly unravels the belt from her own arm and ties it around Maytha's leg, making a tourniquet. She picks her up and leans her back against a tree, and places the sword next to her for any further defense she might need.<br>
<br>
~If you need anything else, just scream...~<br>
<br>
Varia vaults back up on her horse and turns him around to scan the field, looking for anyone who might need assistance. <p><html> <font face="Signet Roundhand ATT"> Varia Angelina Avande </font> </html></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6A74B4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenmaytha.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Queen Maytha</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 28<br> <font color=#FFFF00>(11/23/01 5:43 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=7.topic&index=185>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/amznqnmay/smallmaytha.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Maytha</span><hr size=1> Sees Varia come and pull the sword out from her leg. Maytha screamed a bit from the pain. She then gets placed leaning against the tree....Maytha looked at Varia, &quot;Thanks....&quot; Maytha said, still in pain. Sees Varia gallop off. Maytha tears off her clothing, wrapping her wound, over the belt varia put in. to stop the bleeding from on her leg to the floor. Maytha grabs more arrows and a bow....she then uses the sword to push herself up, grunts in pain as she stands. She uses the sword as a cane, then leans her body on the tree. She peeks thru and loads up her bow. She gets ready when she sees any intruder comeing towards her amazon sisters.... <p><FONT SIZE="10"><FONT FACE="WingDings">Z</FONT></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6A74B4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenvaria.showPublicProfile?language=EN>QueenVaria</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://Windows/Desktop/Tsianina/tsianina2.art" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 74<br> <font color=#FFFF00>(11/23/01 6:05 pm)</font><br>   <a hr