<br>
'Nice attack.' ::He said as blood came forth from the wound. <br>
<br>
He assumed a fighting stance with his legs spread and slightly squat, eyes on Alastor then the cry of the familiar war god caught his attention. His eyes darted to the charging god and Poseidon pointed his glowing trident to the ground before Ares. The earth itself unfolded itself and surrounds the war god. Earth falls from earth as it lifts over itself and encloses around the god. Then the earth round Ares glows white and blows up with a deafening blast.<br>
<br>
Then he turned back to Alastor tucked his trident under his slightly bleeding wound and charges him. He stops right before Alastor and feints a kick to him, then he thrusts the trident straight at Alastor's abdomen grunting as the healing wound reopened and the blood flowed anew.:: <p>Poseidon~Lord of the Deep Blue Sea~Patron Of Horses And Sailors~</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6A74B4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uxgoddessaphrodite.showPublicProfile?language=EN>xGoddess Aphrodite</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 142<br> <font color=#FFFF00>(11/23/01 9:17 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=7.topic&index=189>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.xenafan.com/gallery/if_the_shoe_fits/itsf254aphrodite27.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Make love not war...</span><hr size=1> :::Aphrodite frowns at the horrid display of violence that is taking place before her.  Seeing her friends fighting each other makes her feel pain.  She looks over to Zephyr and motions that she will be leaving:::  <br>
